{"3512410": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Hentai Natsuki", "steam_appid": 3512410, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hentai Natsuki</strong> 是一款令人興奮的遊戲，融合了豐富的情色內容、燒腦謎題、引人入勝的劇情和感性的氛圍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲的主角是迷人的 <strong>Natsuki</strong>——一位勇敢、性感的特工，精通武器使用，總是願意冒險執行危險任務。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512410/extras/6b7534a8313334ee795fadcf5e0e0213.poster.avif?t=1755420187\" width=640 height=130 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512410/extras/6b7534a8313334ee795fadcf5e0e0213.webm?t=1755420187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3512410/extras/6b7534a8313334ee795fadcf5e0e0213.mp4?t=1755420187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，她最強大的武器不僅僅是她在戰鬥中的專業能力，還有她天生的魅力，能夠輕易俘獲男人的心。她知道如何吸引目光，即使在最危險的情況下，也能營造誘人的氛圍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三種難度選擇：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>簡單</strong> – 適合喜歡快速解謎並享受內容的玩家。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>中等</strong> – 在有趣的挑戰與遊戲樂趣之間取得平衡。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>困難</strong> – 適合喜愛嚴謹智力挑戰的玩家。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30個關卡；</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30個成就；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >畫廊；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多種難度級別；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放鬆且浪漫的音樂。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解開謎題，解鎖激情場景，深入了解迷人的 <strong>Natsuki</strong>。<strong>Hentai Natsuki</strong> 是一款令人沉迷、充滿誘惑